    "description": "Corrupted Beats is a high-stakes roguelite survival game where you'll have to face an endless barrage of enemies driven by the pulsing beat of the music. As you fight to survive in procedurally generated worlds, you'll have the chance to upgrade your character with unique equipment and weapons, customize your appearance with different colors and skins, and unlock permanent upgrades to help you make it further each time you play. Plus, you can easily add your own music to the game to enjoy as you take on the corrupted beats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/4b8d9d07240d84c88762691f0c54c800.avif?t=1677843226\" width=400 height=85 /></span><br>Engage in a relentless battle against an endless onslaught of foes surrounded by mesmerizing and electrifying neon graphics that enhance the gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/5bfa5b224983ca2655833de39737f3b3.poster.avif?t=1677843226\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/5bfa5b224983ca2655833de39737f3b3.webm?t=1677843226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/5bfa5b224983ca2655833de39737f3b3.mp4?t=1677843226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/2f5836cd92741b8537549e11697b6fc3.avif?t=1677843226\" width=400 height=85 /></span><br>Experience an electrifying battle against music-synced enemies and add your own tracks to create unique patterns every round, customizing your gaming adventure like never before.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/7507c3a642694fe8d4e01118d6a622b0.poster.avif?t=1677843226\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/7507c3a642694fe8d4e01118d6a622b0.webm?t=1677843226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/7507c3a642694fe8d4e01118d6a622b0.mp4?t=1677843226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/2de96364aa061b8f216ec4365160a752.avif?t=1677843226\" width=400 height=85 /></span><br>Enhance your character's abilities by equipping an extensive selection of distinctive equipment and weapons, and acquire upgrades after each run to unleash your full combat potential and conquer increasingly challenging levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/4a982004d57a8034836c97e676628eb0.avif?t=1677843226\" width=428 height=512 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/b723aadcd88693406b7139af298badf6.avif?t=1677843226\" width=400 height=85 /></span><br>Personalize your character with a range of colors and skins to suit your style<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/58ee5e944b4caa989d8a2a836f3d1aae.poster.avif?t=1677843226\" width=216 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169940/extras/58ee5e944b4caa989d8a2a836f3d1aae.webm?t=167